<body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>行<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>列の行列</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="lsub"><munit> </munit></mlink><mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>の各成分は独立であるものと仮定し、シュミットの方法でそれぞれの成分を正規直交ベクトル</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>に変換する。</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">vdots</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">k</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>まず、<mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>に着目。<mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>は<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>から「<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>の<mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>方向に平行な成分」を引いたベクトル、すなわち平行四辺形の面積を「底辺の長さ×高さ」として<mblock><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>の絶対値を底辺の長さとすると、<mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>の長さは高さに相当する。故に、<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>と<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>で構成される平行四辺形の面積(底辺の長さ×高さ)は、<mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>と<mblock><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>で構成される長方形の面積と等しい。同様の議論を繰り返していくと、</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="lsub"><munit> </munit></mlink><mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>で構成される平行<mblock><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>面体の体積は、</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>で構成される超直方体の体積と等しくなることが分かる。超直方体の体積は、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">prod<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">k</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mblock></p>
<p>になる。</p>
<p>さて、</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>の行列式をシュミットの方法と絡めながら求める。</p>
<p>行列式においてある列を<mblock><munit italic="1">c</munit></mblock>倍すると元の行列式の<mblock><munit italic="1">c</munit></mblock>倍になるから、</p>
<p><mblock><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock> <mblock><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><tex>\left|</tex><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><tex>\right|</tex></mblock></p>
<p>またある列を何倍かしたものを別の列に足しても行列式の値は変わらないから、</p>
<p><mblock><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><tex>\left|</tex><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>|</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><tex>\right|</tex><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><tex>\left|</tex><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><tex>\right|</tex></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">vdots</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">k</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">prod<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">k</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray></mblock></p>
<p>を得る。正規直交ベクトルで構成された行列</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>は直交行列</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">U<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">t</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">E</munit></mblock></p>
<p>を成し、<mblock><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>|</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">pm</munit><munit>1</munit></mblock></p>
<p>である。よって</p>
<p><mblock><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>|</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">prod<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">k</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">k</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="vert"><melem/></marray></mblock></p>
<p>を得る。すなわち、</p>
<p><mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>の行列式の絶対値は、これが成す平行<mblock><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>面体の体積と等しい。</p>
